<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV76">
<l>iṭampōy virintiv vulakaḷan tāṉeḻi lārtaṇṭuḻāy</l>
<l>vaṭampō tiṉaiyu maṭaneñca mēnaṅkaḷ veḷvaḷaikkē</l>
<l>viṭampōl virita lituviyap pēviyaṉ ṟāmaraiyiṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṭampō toṭuṅkamel lāmpal lalarvikkum veṇṭiṅkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Foolish heart that despairs for the buds from the strands of beautiful cool</l>
<l>Tulsi, of him who went for the place [and], expanding, measured this world,</l>
<l>spreading like a poison to our white bangles, this is miraculous, the white moon</l> 
<l>that makes the soft white lotus bloom, for the broad buds of the wide day lotus to be restrained.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
